I"I<h1 id="how-to-add-a-sponsors-listing-to-my-event">How to add a sponsors listing to my event?</h1>

<h2 id="to-add-sponsor-listing-you-need-to">To add sponsor listing, you need to:</h2>

<h3 id="1-log-into-eventyay">1. Log into <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Eventyay</code></h3>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-1.png" alt="Logging-in" /></p>

<h3 id="2-select-manage-event">2. Select <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">manage event</code></h3>

<p>On the top right hand corner of the page, right click your <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">username</code>, choose <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">manage event</code>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-2.png" alt="Manage-event-dropdown" /></p>

<h3 id="3-go-to-event-dashboard">3. Go to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">event dashboard</code></h3>

<p>Choose the event you want to add sponsors for and select <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">event dashboard</code>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-3.png" alt="Clicking-event-dashboard" /></p>

<h3 id="4-adding-sponsors">4. Adding sponsors</h3>

<p>On the overview menu, scroll down, on the right hand corner, choose <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">add sponsors</code>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-4.png" alt="Adding sponsors" /></p>

<h3 id="5-turn-on-sponsors">5. Turn on sponsors</h3>

<p>After you choose <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">add sponsors</code>, it will bring you to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sponsor custom form</code>, select <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">turn on sponsors</code>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-5.png" alt="Turn-on-sponsors" /></p>

<h3 id="6-filling-information">6. Filling information</h3>

<p>Put in the information for name, level, type (Diamond, Platinum, Gold, Silver…) and the sponsor website’s.</p>

<p>You can always add a short abstract or description about your sponsor. You can choose your sponsor’s logo (remember to ensure the size is no bigger than 1MB for best resolution).</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-6.png" alt="Adding-Sponsor-information" /></p>

<p>After putting all needed information, this is what it should look like.</p>

<p><img src="/images/How-to-add-sponsors-listing-to-my-event-7.png" alt="After-adding-Sponsor-information" /></p>

<h3 id="7-saving-your-changes">7. Saving your changes</h3>

<p>When you are done, you can choose to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">publish</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">save draft</code> in case you want to do any editing later on.</p>
:ET